{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/common-responses.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Common responses provide consistent messaging across the platform and prevent you from having to write out the same message again and again. When you select an action for a report, you can have a common response pre-populate for that specific action.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"common-response-1\"\n        title=\"common-response-1\"\n        src=\"/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/0b533/common-response-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/fac75/common-response-1.png 125w,\n/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/63868/common-response-1.png 250w,\n/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/0b533/common-response-1.png 500w,\n/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/1d69c/common-response-1.png 750w,\n/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/00d43/common-response-1.png 1000w,\n/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/97a96/common-response-1.png 2400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3><a id=\"set-up-a-default-common-response\">Set Up a Default Common Response</a></h3>\n<br>To set a default common response:\n<br><br>1. Go to <b>Settings > Program > Automation > Common Responses</b>.\n<br>2. You'll find a pre-populated list of responses that HackerOne finds useful.\n<br>3. Click the <b>Set default Common Responses</b> button.\n<br>4. In the <b>Default Common Responses</b> window, select the default response message from the drop-down next to the action.\n<br>5. Click <b>Save</b>.\n<p>The default common response will automatically populate when you select the action for the report.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 493px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 142.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"common-response-2\"\n        title=\"common-response-2\"\n        src=\"/static/b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d/f88d0/common-response-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d/fac75/common-response-2.png 125w,\n/static/b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d/63868/common-response-2.png 250w,\n/static/b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d/f88d0/common-response-2.png 493w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3><a id=\"add-your-own-common-response\">Add Your Own Common Response</a></h3>\nYou can write your own common response\nTo add a new common response:\n1. Go to **Settings > Program > Automation > Common Responses**.\n2. Select the **Add Common Response** button.\n3. Type the title of your response in the **Common Response Title** field. This title will show up in the list of common responses to choose from.\n4. Type the message of your response in the **Message** field.\n5. Click **Create Common Response**.\n<p>Your common response will display in the list of common responses to choose from when you set up a default common response.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"common-response-3\"\n        title=\"common-response-3\"\n        src=\"/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/0b533/common-response-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/fac75/common-response-3.png 125w,\n/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/63868/common-response-3.png 250w,\n/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/0b533/common-response-3.png 500w,\n/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/1d69c/common-response-3.png 750w,\n/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/00d43/common-response-3.png 1000w,\n/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/6f464/common-response-3.png 1464w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3><a id=\"edit-a-common-response\">Edit a Common Response</a></h3>\nTo edit a common response:\n1. Go to **Settings > Program > Automation > Common Responses**.\n2. Click the title of the response you want to edit.\n3. Edit the title and the message.\n4. Click **Update Common Response**.","frontmatter":{"path":"/programs/common-responses.html","id":"programs/common-responses","title":"Common Responses","description":null},"headings":[]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}